{
  "stem": "15943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 24.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She said, I'll give it to him after the winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it's December.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Mm-mm, she didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the funny part is he took that oven, put it around with string, took it to the wagon, and it fell apart.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] Montezuma's revenge-- he didn't, he didn't have the oven.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have the oven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she just stood by, didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- so whatever, I don't know if she suddenly-- because she got the power or the, the, the, the hate, did the anti-Semitism was there, and it just blossomed when she had a chance?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before that there was no anti-Semitism from her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was like a nasty grandmother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's, that's what we thought.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because she kept always bossing us around, very strict.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was-- for better or for worse, she was helpful and sitting with my mother and talking things and friends advice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's scary to see how people could change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] She was very upset and very disappointed because she kind of-- she was close to that woman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She knew her all her life-- very upsetting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she felt very betrayed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was betrayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt the same thing, betrayed from [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Harry, ?] when he could come and tell us the Jews are parasites.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jews are responsible for the evil.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you were raised like a Jewish child here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was more Jew than whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They never went to church.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only time they celebrate it was Christmas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he had the Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, I didn't have a Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had fun helping him decorate it because Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Gruber, being that she had more money, she would buy the ornaments and chocolate.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
